I&#39;ve only seen a station or control center in a dream. I was given a tour and I was floating, I could not detect that I had a body. The place looked like a combination, lab, dispatch center and control room. It was fairly crowded and there were many what I would call technicians or engineers looking at various equipment, monitoring equipment.  Frank R was interested in heterodyne messages, I got another last night.
&quot;Thanks to David heterodyne&quot;

Dave

